# ADCopyPaste - Changelog

## [1.0.2] - 2026-03-04
- Refactored to follow ADToolkit's conventions

## [1.0.1]
- Fixed reconnection edge cases on paste.

## [1.0.0]
- Initial release.
- Copy and paste nodes while preserving their input connections, even when upstream nodes are not selected.
- Clone detection to avoid reconnection conflicts.
- Compatible with Nuke Indie and Non-Commercial via TCL-based workarounds.
